but the timing isn't right.

52:28.661 --> 52:31.194
They... They have to part.

52:31.196 --> 52:33.429
And then,

52:33.431 --> 52:35.565
years later, they...
They meet again.

52:35.567 --> 52:37.333
They get another chance.

52:39.570 --> 52:43.506
You know, but they don't know
if too much time has passed.

52:43.508 --> 52:46.276
If they waited too long,
if it's,

52:46.278 --> 52:48.344
you know,

52:48.346 --> 52:50.446
too late to make it work.

