53:35.994 --> 53:39.295
I was completely in love
with this guy.

53:40.865 --> 53:43.800
He played guitar, and, um,

53:43.802 --> 53:45.168
I ran away from home

53:45.170 --> 53:48.972
and, uh, went to San Francisco
so I could go live with him.

53:50.775 --> 53:54.277
Yeah, he convinced me
I had a beautiful voice,

53:54.279 --> 53:57.680
and I, uh... I dreamed
of becoming a singer.

53:59.984 --> 54:01.818
I love San Francisco.

54:01.820 --> 54:05.655
Yeah, he was...
He was my first love.

54:05.657 --> 54:07.791
Probably the only one.

54:09.961 --> 54:11.327
He must have been a great guy.

54:11.329 --> 54:14.397
I don't...
I don't know, I...

54:14.399 --> 54:17.834
He may have been. It didn't last
long enough for me to find out.

54:17.836 --> 54:20.904
Yeah. Truth is, I...

54:20.906 --> 54:24.307
I can't even remember
what he looked like.

54:24.309 --> 54:26.209
Really?
Yeah.

54:26.211 --> 54:28.111
That's too bad.

54:28.113 --> 54:31.648
My dad...
My dad showed up, actually.

54:31.650 --> 54:32.649
You were in trouble.

54:32.651 --> 54:33.650
Yeah, he came in.

54:33.652 --> 54:34.651
Yeah, I was in trouble.

54:34.653 --> 54:37.353
He yanked me back to Chicago.

54:37.355 --> 54:40.157
Yeah.

54:40.159 --> 54:42.592
And he was sick, and he, uh...

54:42.594 --> 54:43.726
He had these...

54:43.728 --> 54:47.264
These dreams of me becoming
a doctor, you know?

54:50.567 --> 54:54.104
You know, and eventually,
they became my dreams too.

54:57.675 --> 54:59.109
He was right.

55:00.744 --> 55:03.613
You know, I...
I feel good helping people.

55:11.222 --> 55:12.588
Then he died.

55:18.362 --> 55:19.495
Kate.

55:22.533 --> 55:23.867
What?

55:31.175 --> 55:32.575
(SIGHS)

55:32.577 --> 55:34.244
I, uh...

55:37.048 --> 55:38.815
You...?

