PLAYING)

01:09:28.278 --> 01:09:29.645
(BIRDS CHIRPING)

01:09:37.287 --> 01:09:40.055
<i>♪ I saw it written</i>
<i>And I saw it say ♪</i>

01:09:43.225 --> 01:09:46.627
<i>♪ Pink moon is on its way</i>

01:09:49.032 --> 01:09:52.801
<i>♪ And none of you</i>
<i>Stand so tall ♪</i>

01:09:55.672 --> 01:09:58.307
Pick a place.
I'll be there, I promise.

01:09:58.309 --> 01:09:59.842
Tomorrow, what do you say?

01:09:59.844 --> 01:10:01.543
But, Alex,
